Reasoning: 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on the impact of notifications on human behavior and productivity. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is also likely as the paper discusses the social implications of notifications and their effect on social connections. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as the paper touches on the impact of notifications on social interactions. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) could be relevant as the paper discusses the design and management of notifications. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper could be seen as analyzing the complexity of managing notifications and their impact on productivity.
